description: Full planning application for the erection of a 31-storey tower plus basement (max. 116.620 above OS datum) to provide 190 residential units comprising of 19 x studios, 73 x 1-bedroom, 80 x 2-bedroom, 18 x 3-bedroom units and 1019 sqm of flexible A1/A2/A3/A4/A5/B1 commercial floorspace, together with landscaping and public realm improvements and four number car parking spaces (total of 80 car parking spaces at basement level).
decision_conditions:
CONDITION: The development hereby permitted shall be begun not later than the expiration of three years from the date of this permission.
	
REASON: To comply with the provisions of Section 91(1)(a) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 as amended by the Planning and Compulsory Purchase Act 2004 (Chapter 5).
